                        <p style="color: var(--slate-600); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 1rem; padding-right: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">CFD Penney is a free, open-source collaborative annotation tool that enables real-time drawing, screen sharing, video calls, and Teams-style chat messaging. You can draw on whiteboards, annotate shared screens, or use the infinite canvas mode for unlimited creative space. No account required.</p>
                    </div>
