                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)" style="width: 100%; text-align: left; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0;">
                        <h4 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--slate-900); margin: 0;">Is CFD Penney free to use?</h4>
