                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer" style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out; padding-top: 0;">
                        <p style="color: var(--slate-600); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 1rem; padding-right: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">Yes, CFD Penney is completely free forever. There are no hidden costs, no subscriptions, and no account registration required. The service is open-source and available for anyone to use.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                <div class="faq-item reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-200); padding: 1.5rem 0;">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)" style="width: 100%; text-align: left; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0;">
                        <h4 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--slate-900); margin: 0;">Do I need to create an account?</h4>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon" style="color: var(--brand-600); transition: transform 0.3s;"></i>
