                        <p style="color: var(--slate-600); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 1rem; padding-right: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">No, CFD Penney does not require any account creation or login. You can start collaborating immediately by hosting a session or joining with a 6-character session code. No personal information is collected.</p>
